description: HUTN, Inc. does not have significant operations. The company intends to identify potential merger partners and/or acquirers for selected company assets. Previously, it was engaged in the provision of digital finance and investment services. The company was formerly known as EF Hutton America, Inc. and changed its name to HUTN, Inc. in October 2017. HUTN, Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Springfield, Ohio.
